OL,3,CMan 'devastated' after council orders
OL,4,Cremoval of rooftop garden
OL,6,FA Devon businessman says he is
OL,7,F"absolutely devastated" and will
OL,8,F"fight tooth and nail" to keep his
OL,9,Frooftop garden after he was ordered to
OL,10,Fremove it by the council.
OL,12,FRob Wood runs Broadsands Beach
OL,13,FWatersports Centre in Paignton. He
OL,14,Fstarted a garden on the site's roof
OL,15,Fearlier this year.
OL,17,FHe said the feature has become so
OL,18,Fpopular that people have started
OL,19,Fcontributing their own items, turning
OL,20,Fit into a Mediterranean-style garden.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
