OL,3,CMan 'devastated' after council orders
OL,4,Cremoval of rooftop garden
OL,6,FBut Torbay Council now says the roof
OL,7,Fgarden was made without prior
OL,8,Fpermission and could pose potential
OL,9,Frisks.
OL,11,F"I'm devastated," Rob said. "I'm not
OL,12,Fgoing to lie, I'm absolutely
OL,13,Fdevastated.
OL,15,F"When I told the lads they couldn't
OL,16,Fbelieve it.
OL,18,F"We poured our heart and soul into
OL,19,Fthis just for us to be told to take it
OL,20,Fdown.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
