OL,3,CMan 'devastated' after council orders
OL,4,Cremoval of rooftop garden
OL,6,F"We hoped there'd be a sensible
OL,7,Fcompromise and not just a blanket ban."
OL,9,FThe area is not open to the public but
OL,10,FRob says it used to be hotspot for
OL,11,Fantisocial activity - until his
OL,12,Frenovations.
OL,14,FHe has not just been planting flowers,
OL,15,Fbut he's also been growing fruit and
OL,16,Fvegetables too.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
