OL,3,CMan 'devastated' after council orders
OL,4,Cremoval of rooftop garden
OL,6,FThe seating in the garden has been
OL,7,Fmade up with pallets from South West
OL,8,FWater which were used in the emergency
OL,9,Fdistribution of water during the
OL,10,Fcryptosporidium outbreak earlier this
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FHe said: "We just started planting a
OL,14,Ffew flowers in March. We got some
OL,15,Fpallets and made them into planters
OL,16,Fand everything started growing.
OL,18,F"People from the local area started
OL,19,Fgiving us bits and bobs like cuttings
OL,20,Fand things like that.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
