OL,3,CMan 'devastated' after council orders
OL,4,Cremoval of rooftop garden
OL,6,F"We popped the seeds onto the roof as
OL,7,Fit's a nice little suntrap. Then we
OL,8,Ffound a boat on Facebook Marketplace
OL,9,Fand added things I've collected over
OL,10,Fthe last 17 years.
OL,12,F"It's become very much like a
OL,13,Fcommunity thing, with the fact that
OL,14,Fpeople come and look at it and
OL,15,Fcontribute bits and bobs to it."
OL,17,FRob said he was visited by a member of
OL,18,FTorbay Council on Monday 19 August and
OL,19,Fwas told there had been a number of
OL,20,Fcomplaints.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
