OL,3,CMan 'devastated' after council orders
OL,4,Cremoval of rooftop garden
OL,6,FHe said: "A lady from the council came
OL,7,Fdown and told me that the garden
OL,8,Fneeded to go. She said it had had lots
OL,9,Fof complaints and they said they had
OL,10,Fhad no emails in support.
OL,12,F"There was no negotiation. It was just
OL,13,F'the garden has to go'. They said it
OL,14,Fwas under health and safety grounds,
OL,15,Fincluding edge protection.
OL,17,F"I said, in which case, I'll install
OL,18,Fsome rope and some posts around it.
OL,19,FThen they said it was the weight of
OL,20,Fthe garden.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
