OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F436A1724524215
OL,3,CMan 'devastated' after council orders
OL,4,Cremoval of rooftop garden
OL,6,F"I'm a civil engineer by trade and
OL,7,Fthere's no issue with weight. I've
OL,8,Fused my experience to ensure that's
OL,9,Fnot the case.
OL,11,F"Every single day, I am bombarded with
OL,12,Fcompliments about it. People go round
OL,13,Fthere everyday, there's always someone
OL,14,Flooking at it, always someone taking
OL,15,Fphotos, people taking videos.
OL,17,F"A lady was live on FaceTime to her
OL,18,Fsister in Brazil, talking about how
OL,19,Fwonderful this Mediterranean roof
OL,20,Fgarden was in Torbay.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
