OL,3,CMan 'devastated' after council orders
OL,4,Cremoval of rooftop garden
OL,6,F"If they have an issue with it, why
OL,7,Fcan't they come and say 'can we do
OL,8,Fthis instead?' I'm just really
OL,9,Fdisappointed by the 'get rid of it'
OL,10,Fattitude."
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the authority said:
OL,13,F"We acknowledge the efforts of a
OL,14,Ftenant on our property, who has
OL,15,Fconstructed a roof garden without
OL,16,Fprior permission.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
