OL,3,CMan 'devastated' after council orders
OL,4,Cremoval of rooftop garden
OL,6,F"While we appreciate Mr Wood's
OL,7,Fpositive intentions, it is crucial to
OL,8,Femphasise that any modifications to
OL,9,Fleased properties must comply with
OL,10,Fplanning, structural safety, and
OL,11,Fhealth and safety regulations.
OL,13,F"It is never our intention to limit
OL,14,Finitiatives for things such as
OL,15,Fgardens, however, as a responsible
OL,16,Fauthority, we must ensure that all
OL,17,Fadditions to our properties are safe
OL,18,Fand compliant with structural safety
OL,19,Fand health and safety regulations.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
