OL,3,CMan 'devastated' after council orders
OL,4,Cremoval of rooftop garden
OL,6,F"Allowing unapproved modifications
OL,7,Fwhich deviate from lease conditions
OL,8,Fcould pose potential risks to Mr Wood,
OL,9,Fthe area, and all users of that area.
OL,11,F"We hope to resolve this matter
OL,12,Famicably and encourage Mr Wood to
OL,13,Fengage with us through the proper
OL,14,Fchannels for any future initiatives."
OL,16,FRob added: "I'm going to fight tooth
OL,17,Fand nail to make sure it doesn't go.
OL,18,FIt was a verbal order, rather than a
OL,19,Fprohibition notice or anything like
OL,20,Fthat.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
